        <bioghist id="ref3">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>James Madison was the fourth President of the United States and was elected to the American Philosophical Society in 1785.</p>
        </bioghist>
        <odd id="ref17">
            <head>Early American History Note</head>
            <p>These two volumes record the daily weather and other data at James Madison's plantation Montpeiler. In addition to the meteorological data, there are occasionally other notes pertaining to gardening and harvesting. These annotations often note the plants they have and where they were on the grounds.</p>
